can anyone give me a simple recipe please can someone please give me a idea on tonights dinner plan give me a easy recipe beef stroganoff ingredients ounce package egg noodles pound ground beef ounce can fat free condensed cream of mushroom soup tablespoon garlic powder cup sour cream salt and pepper to taste directions prepare the egg noodles according to package directions and set aside in a separate large skillet over medium heat saute the ground beef over medium heat for to minutes or until browned drain the fat and add the soup and garlic powder simmer for minutes stirring occasionally remove from heat and combine the meat mixture with the egg noodles add the sour cream stirring well and season with salt and pepper to taste serve with some garlic bread and enjoy Japanese cuisine Cantonese cuisine Breakfast Chili con carne Tofu Russian cuisine Ramen Cuisine of Denmark Korean cuisine Cuisine of Malaysia Chicken soup Cajun cuisine Hamburger Barbecue Bread German cuisine Jewish cuisine Kraft Dinner Cuisine of Laos French fries Polish cuisine Curry Soup Peruvian cuisine Cuisine of Brazil Bengali cuisine Dumpling French cuisine Coffee Beef noodle soup Haggis Cuisine of Thailand Pizza Pot Noodle Cincinnati chili Vegetarian cuisine Cuisine of Vietnam Mayonnaise Cha chaan teng MRE Idli Gumbo Cuisine of Singapore Pasta Recipe Soul food Roast beef American Chinese cuisine Pancake Sichuan Pepper Dairy Chocolate Tea Nabemono Dim sum Cuisine of Cambodia Tamale Goulash Canadian Chinese cuisine Cuisine of the Southern United States Hot dog D__ner kebab Menudo (soup) Yoghurt Sushi Vegetarianism Roman eating and drinking Bacon Hot pot Satay Brewery Cuisine of Turkey Food Laksa Ketchup Cuisine of Austria Consomm__ Italian cuisine Corned beef Cooking weights and measures Soy protein Donburi Ukrainian cuisine Cooking Salad Meatball Bagel Stir frying Domesticated turkey Turkish coffee 